description: Perfectly located on one of the most vibrant streets in South Boston, this stunning two bedroom, two bathroom home is a one-of-a-kind opportunity to live a life of luxury with the city at your fingertips! The spacious floor plan features an open living/dining room with a gorgeous gas fireplace, oversized windows, and an eat-in breakfast bar. The modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space. Top it off with hardwood floors throughout, extra storage space, garage parking, and sweeping views of the Boston skyline. With easy access to public transportation and a wide variety of restaurants, bars, and shops that East Broadway is known for,  this home is perfect for anyone looking to live in one of the most highly sought after neighborhoods in all of Boston.
